      "Hyperscalers are on pace for ~$500B in global compute capex.",
      "Enterprise ROI remains elusive at best, absent at worst.",
      "MIT research found 95% of enterprise generative AI pilots deliver no measurable P&L impact. Only 5% of integrated systems created significant value.",
      "That gap is fueling boardroom talk of a modern Tulip Mania. But the comparison misses something basic.",
      "When a bubble in perishable assets pops, you’re left with rotting bulbs. When infrastructure corrects, the assets stay. The risk is nonetheless real.",
