      "Data centers can be built in 18 months. Power grids often take 5–7 years to catch up.",
      "That mismatch is forcing complex financing just to dodge grid backlogs.",
      "A major correction is coming.",
      "The better analogy than tulips is the Dot-Com crash or Railway Mania ie non-perishable asset speculation.",
