      "Today’s data centers and grid upgrades may play the same role.",
      "The lesson isn’t that AI infrastructure is a fad.",
      "It’s that capital speed must eventually meet cash-flow reality.",
      "The bubble may leak or collapse entirely taking many investors money with it.",
      "The accompanying concrete and silicon stay.",
      "The real question: who converts that capital into durable cash flow and who loses money- lots of money?",
